headline: Lockheed Martin Leads "Almost Exclusively Buy-Rated" Defense Stocks Set To Report
summary: Analysts see positive drivers for defense earnings next week. Lockheed Martin, RTX, Northrop Grumman kick off results on Tuesday.

headline: Boeing Inks Deal to Supply Up to 18 787 Dreamliners to Gulf Air
summary: BA signs a deal with Gulf Air to supply up to 18 787 Dreamliners, boosting its commercial business backlog and global fleet momentum.
